  typingSpeed: 0.05
  fullMessage: "Karakterin g\xF6revi, bu ki\u015Filerin zihinlerini okuyarak dertlerini
    \xF6\u011Frenmek ve cad\u0131n\u0131n verdi\u011Fi 5 iksir aras\u0131ndan do\u011Fru
    olan\u0131 se\xE7ip onlara sunmakt\u0131r. anla\u015F\u0131lan \xE7e\u015Fitli
    dertlerinin olmas\u0131d\u0131r."
  silinmeSuresi: 2
  baslangicGecikmesi: 17
